    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The condition of being understandable in two or more ways, as, for example in two or more different social or historical contexts, or of referring to two or more things at the same time.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
